title: SEP Sesam License Expiry
agents: sep_sesam
catalog: app/backup
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check monitors the SEP Sesam maintenance license expiration date via
 the SEP Sesam REST API.

 The number of remaining days is compared against configurable thresholds:
 - OK:       More days remaining than the warning threshold
 - WARNING:  Days remaining within the warning threshold (default: 30 days)
 - CRITICAL: Days remaining within the critical threshold (default: 15 days)
 - CRITICAL: License already expired

 Thresholds can be adjusted via the "SEP Sesam License Expiry" rule.

 Requires the SEP Sesam special agent to be configured for the host.

discovery:
 One service is created per SEP Sesam host.
